 of how to achieve such a climate in Vietnam is essential to an assessment of the country’s prospects now and into the 21st century.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aInvestments, ForeignzVietnam. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Money & Monetary Policy.2bisacsh1 aChi, Bui Kim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDoanh, Le Dang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDung, Nguyen Tuan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKhiem, Nguyen Tri, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeung, Suiwah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeung, Suiwah, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMaitland, Elizabth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVasavakul, Thaveeporn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertISEAS Archive eBook-Package 1970-1999z978311060669040uhttps://doi.org/10.1355/978981434591040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789814345910423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789814345910.jpg  a978-3-11-060669-0  ISEAS Archive eBook-Package 1970-1999c1970d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK